          "title": "∞-DIFF: INFINITE RESOLUTION DIFFUSION",
          "summary": "∞-Diff is introduced as a novel generative diffusion model that operates on infinite resolution data, learning a continuous function for sampling at any resolution. This approach surpasses other infinite resolution models by working directly on raw data, yielding higher sample quality and scaling effectively to resolutions beyond the training data.",
